electronic warfare.

43
00:04:44,750 --> 00:04:47,958
And the mightiest and
deadliest of all the Angeloids,

44
00:04:48,041 --> 00:04:51,625
type Alpha,
my darling Ikaros.

45
00:04:57,750 --> 00:05:00,083
Unlike the other Angeloids
with which we have

46
00:05:00,166 --> 00:05:04,666
filled the Synapse, I created
my daughters to be warriors.

47
