55
00:07:13,041 --> 00:07:16,375
I'm Hiyori Kazane,
a high school student.

56
00:07:16,458 --> 00:07:19,750
I live in a sleepy town
tucked away up in the mountains.

57
00:07:19,833 --> 00:07:22,333
It's a darling little
place called Sorami,

58
00:07:22,416 --> 00:07:25,625
